      <hedline>
        <hl1>DISPUTE OVER RESTRUCTURING</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <byline class="print_byline">By Sabrina Tavernise</byline>
      <byline class="normalized_byline">Tavernise, Sabrina</byline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Struggle over Russia's most actively traded company, Unified Energy Systems, intensifies after company says it will present reorganization plan to government, despite criticism of plan from foreign investors; plan, which calls for splitting off regional power plants and generators from parent company, has been widely opposed by foreign investors who say it will destroy value of their holdings (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>A struggle over Russia's most actively traded company, Unified Energy Systems, intensified after the company said it would present a reorganization plan to the government tomorrow, despite criticism of the plan from foreign investors. The plan, which calls for splitting off regional power plants and generators from the parent company, has been widely opposed by foreign investors who say it will destroy the value of their holdings.</p>
        <p>Sabrina Tavernise</p>
      </block>
